  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6763.53 sitting below the GEX flip at 6791 in a PIN regime, dealers are long gamma and will sell any rally toward the massive +12.4B wall at 6780 while buying dips toward the -10.2B negative gamma pocket at 6750. The gex_surge event with 177% 1-min change indicates heavy options flow just hit, likely creating this new hedging dynamic that should cap upside momentum near 6780 and provide support around 6750. Key levels to watch: 6750 downside support where dealers become buyers, 6780-6785 resistance zone where dealers turn sellers, and 6791 regime flip that would shift dealer behavior from stabilizing to amplifying.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 6750 and 6780 with limited breakout potential.",
